long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
**THIS EXTENSION ONLY REDIRECTS COMMENT PAGES. SUBREDDIT HOMEPAGES ARE IGNORED**

This extension checks if the opened subreddit is set to private, if so then automatically redirects you to the latest available wayback machine snapshot.

Github repository: https://github.com/saikat0511/reddit-wayback-redirector
